==English==
{{wikipedia}}
===Noun===
'''[[delative]] [[case]]'''

#{{grammar}}: [[case]] used to indicate movement '''from''' a surface. In English, this is usually expressed by the prepositions '''from''' or '''off of''', as in "down off of the house." [[Hungarian]] is a language that uses the delative case.

